<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="9cd46773-a0c4-458f-b723-76590c39e2c3" >

    <h2><a id="support"></a>Resources and support</h2> 
<h3>Academic Accommodation Support</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li><strong>General Inquiries:</strong> <a href="mailto:aasadmin@ryerson.ca">aasadmin@ryerson.ca</a>&nbsp;</li> 
 <li><strong>Student Specific Inquiries:</strong> Academic Accommodation Facilitator listed on the student’s accommodation letter</li> 
 <li><strong>Service Providers (Interpreters, etc.):</strong> <a href="mailto:aasbookings@ryerson.ca">aasbookings@ryerson.ca</a></li> 
 <li><strong>RU Noted Peer Note-taking: </strong><a href="mailto:runoted@ryerson.ca">runoted@ryerson.ca</a></li> 
</ul> 
<h4>Test Centre</h4> 
